data.description: Priced to Sell and ready to move.  Come take a look at this prime property located in Tharptown just outside of town and close to the hospital. This place has plenty of room to host your holidays and summer fun. 3 Bedrooms, 2.5 baths, a sunroom, family/media room, LR, DR, open kitchen, & 1st floor laundry round out the living area while the outside patio area features a built-in grill area, large trex deck with pool, firepit for those cozy evenings and plenty of trees for shade. Call Misty @ 570-274-0937 to schedule your private showing - 24 Hr Notice. *Agents see remarks
